Name: WISH - Paradise High
About the game: Emotional Match 3 Puzzle Game 'WISH - Paradise High'. WISH - Paradise High is a puzzle game that combines visual Nobel elements that foster the appeal of female characters with various personalities. While playing WISH-Paradise High, you can meet women from different professions who you've always wanted to be associated with. Enjoy talking to beautiful women and move their minds while playing puzzle games. If you do your best, you will win Heroin's heart as a reward. All characters related to game contents are adults. Enjoy the new fun with 'WISH - Paradise High'. Thank you. Characteristics - Combination of 3 match puzzle games and visual Nobel elements. Strategies through random quests. - Women of various personalities and tastes appear (will continue to be updated). - Professional voice actors participate. Insert theme OST by character. - Unlockable outfits and a gallery of beautiful women.
